  <!--
    FUZO Food Discovery App - Sitemap & Architecture Overview
    ========================================================
    Entry Point: App.tsx → AuthProvider → PageRouter → (initialPage: "landing")

    Navigation Architecture:
    - Hamburger Menu (Top-left): Access to all pages via PageSelector
    - Bottom Navigation: Feed, Scout, Snap, Bites (on main app pages)
    - Universal Header: Chat, Profile, Hamburger (context-dependent)
    - AI Assistant: Tako floating button (available on all non-landing pages)

    Brand System:
    - Colors: Coral Red (#F14C35), Deep Orange-Brown (#A6471E), Navy (#0B1F3A), Yellow (#FFD74A)
    - Typography: Red Hat Display + Roboto
    - Mascot: Tako the octopus
  -->

