  <!-- NAVIGATION FLOW SUMMARY -->
  <!--
    Primary User Journey:
    1. Landing Page → Onboarding Flow → Feed (main app)
    2. Feed ↔ Scout ↔ Snap ↔ Bites (bottom navigation)
    3. Any page → Chat/Profile (universal header)
    4. Profile → Friend profiles (social flow)
    5. Tako AI Assistant (floating, available everywhere except landing)

    Developer/Admin Journey:
    1. Hamburger Menu → Development pages (diagnostics, testing, setup)
    2. Backend diagnostics → API testing → OAuth setup → Configuration
    3. Figma integration → Component management → Design system sync

    Authentication Flow:
    1. Google OAuth → Supabase Auth → Profile Creation/Retrieval
    2. Fallback profiles for offline/demo mode
    3. Session management with automatic refresh
    4. Popup blocking detection and user guidance

    Backend Architecture:
    - Three-tier: Frontend → Supabase Edge Functions → Database
    - KV Store for flexible data management
    - External API proxy for security
    - File storage in private Supabase buckets
    - Real-time subscriptions for chat and social features
  -->

